  Replaces: %N-tcltk
  Shlibs: %p/lib/tcl8.4/sqlite/libtclsqlite.0.dylib 9.0.0 %n (>= 2.8.16-3)
  Files: lib/tcl8.4
  DocFiles: LICENSE README
